810
00:54:52,539 --> 00:54:54,291
[Min-beom] Attrapez-le ! Allez!

811
00:54:57,002 --> 00:54:59,087
Ouais, allons-y ! Allons-y! Il y a plus !

812
00:54:59,170 --> 00:55:00,338
Gun-woo, vas-y !

813
00:55:06,720 --> 00:55:07,929
