828
00:56:05,153 --> 00:56:07,197
- [tranches de couteau]
- [Du-yeong gémit]

829
00:56:11,201 --> 00:56:12,452
- [tranches de couteau]
- [la femme grogne]

830
00:56:12,535 --> 00:56:14,454
- [hurle de douleur]
- [rires]

831
00:56:15,330 --> 00:56:16,873
- [la femme gémit]
- [Du-yeong grogne]

832
00:56:18,041 --> 00:56:20,835
