852
00:58:04,397 --> 00:58:05,356
Bloquez-le !

853
00:58:11,821 --> 00:58:13,948
Ouais! Tuez-le ! Allez vite !

854
00:58:14,449 --> 00:58:16,201
[gémissant]

855
00:58:20,288 --> 00:58:22,290
[grondant]

856
00:58:26,711 --> 00:58:27,670
[gémissements]

857
00:58:27,754 --> 00:58:29,130
