894
01:00:23,703 --> 01:00:24,787
[Min-beom] Tuez-le !

895
01:00:24,871 --> 01:00:26,080
[souches]

896
01:00:29,876 --> 01:00:32,086
[gémissant] Agh ! Ah !

897
01:00:32,170 --> 01:00:34,130
[les deux crient]

898
01:00:35,298 --> 01:00:36,924
[Woo-jin] Tu fais du bien ! Oui!

899
01:00:37,425 --> 01:00:39,427
[Min-beom] Retournez ! Tuez-le !

900
01:00:40,053 --> 01:00:41,929
